CEO of Wal-Mart Stores, Inc. (2014–present)[edit]
Walmart announced on November 25, 2013, that McMillon would immediately join the company's board of directors,[18] and would replace Mike Duke as Walmart CEO effective on February 1, 2014, becoming the company's fifth-ever chief executive.[4]
