Insider Activity


Individual




C. Douglas McMillon



Mr. C. D. McMillon is on the Board of Directors at Wal-Mart Stores, Inc., Crystal Bridges Museum of American Art, Enactus Group, The Consumer Goods Forum and US-China Business Council. Mr. McMillon was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Wal-Mart International, President & Chief Executive Officer by Sam's West, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Bharti Walmart Pvt Ltd., and a Principal by Wal-Mart Distribution Center. He also served on the board at Massmart Holdings Ltd. and Wal-Mart de México SAB de CV. He received his undergraduate degree from The University of Arkansas and an MBA from The University of Tulsa.



